{"en":[{"id":"25942441","caption_id":"123039","seq":"1","text":"In this year's Annual Letter, Melinda and I take the toughest questions","translate_comment":"","start":"3.429","dur":"4.16","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942442","caption_id":"123039","seq":"2","text":"we get asked and give our answers.","translate_comment":"","start":"7.589","dur":"4.401","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942443","caption_id":"123039","seq":"3","text":"One that's come up for a long time is: as we make the world healthier,","translate_comment":"","start":"11.99","dur":"3.27","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942444","caption_id":"123039","seq":"4","text":"is the population going to get so big that <a href=\"#post_comment_1\">feeding<i class=\"icon-star\"><\/i><\/a> everybody and maintaining the","translate_comment":"","start":"15.26","dur":"5.92","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942445","caption_id":"123039","seq":"5","text":"environment is going to be impossible?","translate_comment":"","start":"21.18","dur":"3.5","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942446","caption_id":"123039","seq":"6","text":"Here we can see a <a href=\"#post_comment_2\">chart<i class=\"icon-star\"><\/i><\/a> that looks at the total world population","translate_comment":"","start":"24.68","dur":"6.03","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942447","caption_id":"123039","seq":"7","text":"over the last several hundred years, and <a href=\"#post_comment_3\">at first glance <i class=\"icon-star\"><\/i><\/a> this is a bit scary.","translate_comment":"","start":"30.71","dur":"5.49","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942448","caption_id":"123039","seq":"8","text":"We go from less than a billion in 1800, and then 3, 4, 5, 6 and 7.4 billion where","translate_comment":"","start":"36.2","dur":"6.41","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942449","caption_id":"123039","seq":"9","text":"we are today is happening even faster.","translate_comment":"","start":"42.61","dur":"3.53","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942450","caption_id":"123039","seq":"10","text":"So, Melinda and I wondered whether providing new medicines and keeping children","translate_comment":"","start":"46.14","dur":"5.65","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942451","caption_id":"123039","seq":"11","text":"alive, would that create more of a population problem?","translate_comment":"","start":"51.79","dur":"3.83","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942452","caption_id":"123039","seq":"12","text":"What we found out is that as health <a href=\"#post_comment_4\">improve<i class=\"icon-star\"><\/i><\/a>, families choose to have less children","translate_comment":"","start":"55.62","dur":"7.14","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942453","caption_id":"123039","seq":"13","text":"and this effect is very, very dramatic.","translate_comment":"","start":"62.76","dur":"4.48","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942454","caption_id":"123039","seq":"14","text":"We find that in every country of the world, this is repeated.","translate_comment":"","start":"67.24","dur":"4.209","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942455","caption_id":"123039","seq":"15","text":"The population growth goes down as we improve health.","translate_comment":"","start":"71.45","dur":"3.43","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942456","caption_id":"123039","seq":"16","text":"So, we've taken that chart that shows the global population growth","translate_comment":"","start":"74.88","dur":"5.25","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942457","caption_id":"123039","seq":"17","text":"and we've actually extended it out all the way to 2100.","translate_comment":"","start":"80.13","dur":"4.98","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942458","caption_id":"123039","seq":"18","text":"And we can see that instead of continuing, it actually <a href=\"#post_comment_5\">flattens out <i class=\"icon-star\"><\/i><\/a>.","translate_comment":"","start":"85.11","dur":"5.41","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942459","caption_id":"123039","seq":"19","text":"Another way to see that is through this rate of population growth.","translate_comment":"","start":"90.52","dur":"3.959","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942460","caption_id":"123039","seq":"20","text":"And you can see that in the 60s that reached a pretty high number,","translate_comment":"","start":"94.479","dur":"4.14","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942461","caption_id":"123039","seq":"21","text":"over 2% per year, and it's now come way, way down.","translate_comment":"","start":"98.619","dur":"5.581","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942462","caption_id":"123039","seq":"22","text":"Now, 11 billion people is still a lot, but the good news is that the faster we improve","translate_comment":"","start":"104.2","dur":"5.489","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942463","caption_id":"123039","seq":"23","text":"health, the faster family size goes down.","translate_comment":"","start":"109.689","dur":"4.859","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null},{"id":"25942464","caption_id":"123039","seq":"24","text":"And so, we can feel great about saving those lives.","translate_comment":"","start":"114.549","dur":"3.601","is_scores":null,"created_at":"1519612118","updated_at":null}],"zh-Hant":[{"id":"26029018","caption_